	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Tips for the bard that duels.  Know your area of combat better then thien enemy.  Get on the good side of its inhabitants.  Use the monsters to your advantage.  I have a win record of 12/0 fighting Rogues, Shadow KNights, Warriors, Rangers, and sigh other bards.  On more than one occation I have feared my combatant into running past monsters which quickly widdled them down.  Use your songs.  PSALM OF WARMTH may only do 6 dmg, but every single wack is 6 points on them. twist with healing it helps even the odds.  Use weapons that are fast and proc. This too will even the odds.  I have brought down the most hauty ogre shadow knight through trickery and mastering the chess board on which I was playing.  There are no duel rules except live or die.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
